data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.8% LOAN  Well appointed, 2628 sq ft, ICF construction, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home has hardwood floors, granite counters, A/C, independent wall heat in every room, 1 year home warranty, a built in pellet stove. two separate living areas if desired (lower level has own entrance and has been used for short term rental etc.,).  master on main floor with a bathroom with a heated tile floor, huge tub and separate walk in shower. The 1/2 +/- acre lot is fenced for small of large pets (owner has no indoor pets) and has an underground sprinkler system, outdoor seating area that's perfect for entertaining, fire pit, insulated garage, a storage building on concrete slab, there is parking for an rv, or as many as 8+ cars with a circle drive. Approx 35 miles to either Missoula/Polson Seller is a licensed Montana Real Estate Broker. Please call Tony Stout at 406-304-1529 or your Real Estate professional to schedule a showing
